1
00:00:02,168 --> 00:00:03,658
“创始吸血鬼”前情提要
MAN: Previously on The Originals.

2
00:00:03,837 --> 00:00:06,328
- 你是克劳斯的父亲
- 你能让我复活
-You're Klaus' father?
-You can bring me back to life.

3
00:00:06,506 --> 00:00:08,474
欢迎来到我的地狱
-(GASPS)
-Welcome to my hell.

4
00:00:08,641 --> 00:00:12,202
你没事了
你是不是梦到我们父亲了？
You're all right.
Have you dreamt of our father?

5
00:00:12,379 --> 00:00:14,540
- 我见到麦可了
- 我最近也经常梦到他
-I saw Mikael.
-I've been dreaming of him, too.

6
00:00:14,714 --> 00:00:17,478
你母亲显然是个极有天赋的女巫
Your mother is clearly
a very gifted witch.

7
00:00:17,650 --> 00:00:20,312
不管我怎么想
结局都是我和我的人会死
Any way I do the math,
it ends with me and my guys dead.

8
00:00:20,487 --> 00:00:22,546
所以不管你和狼人在密谋着什么
So whatever it is you got coming
with the wolves,

9
00:00:22,722 --> 00:00:25,316
你要知道，我会一直奋战到最后一刻
just know that I will fight
until I am dead!

10
00:00:30,663 --> 00:00:31,652
干得漂亮
WOMAN: Nice job.

11
00:00:31,798 --> 00:00:34,665
帮我省了亲自杀死这些吸血鬼的麻烦
You saved me the trouble
of killing all these vampires myself.

12
00:00:37,871 --> 00:00:39,862
那个孩子有女巫的血统
That baby is part witch.

13
00:00:40,040 --> 00:00:42,099
她必须先出生然后再死
She has to be born first
before she can die.

14
00:00:42,275 --> 00:00:44,004
- 不要
- 只能这样了
-No!
-This is the way it had to be.

15
00:00:55,522 --> 00:00:58,980
在给你众多的追求者之一写情书吗？
KLAUS: Writing a love letter
to one of your many suitors?

16
00:00:59,159 --> 00:01:05,894
谁是那个幸运的收信者？
杰克森还是以利亚？
So who's the lucky recipient then.
Jackson or Elijah?

17
00:01:06,066 --> 00:01:09,365
可别说是我
Don't tell me it's me.

18
00:01:09,536 --> 00:01:11,697
我以为我早就出局了呢
I thought I was out of the running
ages ago.

19
00:01:11,871 --> 00:01:14,635
最自大狂奖项要颁给…
The award for biggest ego goes to....

20
00:01:23,716 --> 00:01:25,741
我们的狼宝宝还好吗？
How is our littlest wolf?

21
00:01:27,053 --> 00:01:29,044
你想不想…
Do you want to....

22
00:01:34,594 --> 00:01:36,892
来吧
Come on.

23
00:01:50,610 --> 00:01:53,611
你感觉到了吗？
-(GASPS)
-(LAUGHS) Feel that?

24
00:02:00,353 --> 00:02:02,048
好吧
Right.

25
00:02:03,323 --> 00:02:06,383
我就不打扰你写信了
I'll leave you
to your secret letter then.

26
00:02:16,136 --> 00:02:18,832
亲爱的柔伊
HAYLEY: Dear Zoey.

27
00:02:19,005 --> 00:02:21,633
凯特琳，或是安琪拉
Or Caitlin or Angela.

28
00:02:21,808 --> 00:02:24,470
我亲爱的女儿
To my little girl...

29
00:02:25,612 --> 00:02:28,581
你父亲刚问我这是不是一封情书
your dad just asked
if this was a love letter. (CHUCKLES)

30
00:02:29,682 --> 00:02:32,242
我想也算是吧
I guess it kind of is.

31
00:02:35,054 --> 00:02:37,818
我没有机会认识我母亲
HAYLEY: I never got
to know my mother.

32
00:02:37,991 --> 00:02:40,323
所以我也不知道她怀着我时是什么心情
I have no idea what she must have
felt when she carried me.

33
00:02:40,493 --> 00:02:41,858
放开我，你这贱人！
Let go of me, you bitch!

34
00:02:44,130 --> 00:02:45,688
所以我想写这封信给你
HAYLEY: So I thought
I'd write to you

35
00:02:45,865 --> 00:02:50,859
好让你知道此刻我有多么开心
so that you could know how happy
I am at this very moment.

36
00:02:51,037 --> 00:02:54,200
我和你父亲都迫不及待想见到你
How much your father and I
can't wait to meet you.

37
00:02:56,943 --> 00:02:59,104
我还想向你保证
And I want to make you a promise,

38
00:02:59,279 --> 00:03:02,271
三样我从未有拥有过的东西
three things that you will have
that I never did.

39
00:03:02,448 --> 00:03:04,678
一个安全的家
A safe home,

40
00:03:04,851 --> 00:03:09,254
有人每天说爱你
someone to tell you
that they love you every single day

41
00:03:09,422 --> 00:03:12,118
并且无条件守护着你
and someone to fight for you
no matter what.

42
00:03:14,127 --> 00:03:16,960
换句话说，一个家
HAYLEY: In other words, a family.

43
00:03:17,130 --> 00:03:18,757
就这样了，宝贝女儿
So there you go, baby girl.

44
00:03:18,932 --> 00:03:21,457
其他的就让我们以后一起共同努力吧
The rest we're going to
have to figure out together.

45
00:03:21,634 --> 00:03:24,865
我爱你，妈妈
I love you. Your mom.

46
00:03:28,908 --> 00:03:31,741
你要知道这么做我也很痛苦
You should know
this brings me no joy.

47
00:03:31,911 --> 00:03:34,471
我保证会速战速决的
-I promise I'll make it quick.
-(SCREAMlNG)

48
00:03:34,647 --> 00:03:36,308
我们开始吧
Let's begin, shall we?

49
00:03:36,482 --> 00:03:37,540
不，不要
No, no, no!

50
00:03:37,717 --> 00:03:42,347
片名：创始吸血鬼（第一季）
剧名：生死循环

51
00:03:42,655 --> 00:03:45,146
主演：约瑟夫摩根

52
00:03:45,992 --> 00:03:48,324
主演：丹尼尔吉利斯

53
00:03:49,662 --> 00:03:51,960
主演：菲比托金

54
00:03:53,299 --> 00:03:54,857
卡密
Cami?

55
00:03:55,368 --> 00:03:57,700
天啊
主演：查尔斯麦可戴维斯
Oh, God. What happened?

56
00:03:57,837 --> 00:03:59,566
- 出什么事了？
- 克劳斯
-Klaus.

57
00:03:59,672 --> 00:04:02,266
他们大战了一场，他被咬了
主演：莉雅派普斯
-They fought, and he got bit.

58
00:04:02,442 --> 00:04:03,466
- 马赛尔
- 没事的
-Marcel.
-It's okay.

59
00:04:03,643 --> 00:04:05,804
他也没比我好多少
主演：丹妮儿坎贝尔
I gave as good as I got,

60
00:04:05,845 --> 00:04:08,370
但我们需要克劳斯的血才能治愈
but we need Klaus's blood to heal.

61
00:04:13,820 --> 00:04:16,186
你和克劳斯交手
You fought Klaus.

62
00:04:16,356 --> 00:04:19,348
- 他流血了吗？
- 我确实将他伤得不轻
-Did he bleed?
-I got him pretty good, yeah.

63
00:04:19,525 --> 00:04:21,220
在哪里？
Where?

64
00:04:45,318 --> 00:04:48,116
黛维娜
Uh, Davina.

65
00:04:48,288 --> 00:04:49,448
你在干什么？
What the hell?

66
00:04:49,622 --> 00:04:50,748
小约，你来这里干什么？
Josh, what are you doing here?

67
00:04:50,790 --> 00:04:52,087
我不是叫你好好休息吗？
制片：克里斯多福贺利尔
I told you to rest.

68
00:04:52,125 --> 00:04:53,092
我没事
制片：克里斯多福贺利尔
-I'm fine.

69
00:04:53,126 --> 00:04:54,320
你很快就会产生幻觉了
-You're going to start hallucinating soon.

70
00:04:54,494 --> 00:04:56,894
除非我的幻觉就是
制片：兰斯安德森
I mean, unless I'm hallucinating you

71
00:04:57,063 --> 00:05:00,430
你莫名其妙站在马路中央，念着咒语
standing in the middle of the street
and chanting for no reason. (LAUGHS)

72
00:05:03,136 --> 00:05:04,763
等等，这真的是幻觉吗？
Wait. Am l?

73
00:05:04,937 --> 00:05:07,906
我会救你的
我会救你们所有人
I'm going to save you.
I'm going to save all of you.

74
00:05:09,008 --> 00:05:11,306
制片：邦妮怀斯

75
00:05:23,489 --> 00:05:25,821
编剧：黛安艾德穆强

76
00:05:27,427 --> 00:05:29,622
好吧
导演：麦特海斯廷
Okay.

77
00:05:29,929 --> 00:05:31,590
看来我产生幻觉了
 I am hallucinating.

78
00:05:33,032 --> 00:05:35,830
- 你们都不得好死
- 再用力，宝宝快出来了
-I will bring hell to your doorstep!
-One last push. Baby's almost here.

79
00:05:36,002 --> 00:05:38,869
我要用你们的鲜血沐浴
I will bathe
in rivers of your blood.

80
00:05:39,038 --> 00:05:42,303
- 我看到宝宝了
- 好了，现在用力
-I can see the baby.
-Okay, now push.

81
00:05:42,475 --> 00:05:45,376
- 慢慢来，慢慢来
- 你们都将尖叫着死去
-Gently, gently.
-You will die screaming!

82
00:05:45,545 --> 00:05:47,638
好了
There.

83
00:06:02,795 --> 00:06:04,626
是个漂亮的小女孩
You have a beautiful baby daughter.

84
00:06:10,069 --> 00:06:11,434
清晨月亮落下时
We must start the sacrifice

85
00:06:11,604 --> 00:06:13,469
我们就必须开始献祭
as soon as the moon sets
with the morning sky.

86
00:06:13,639 --> 00:06:15,106
求求你
Please.

87
00:06:15,274 --> 00:06:17,299
能让我抱抱她吗？
Please, can I hold her?

88
00:06:35,695 --> 00:06:37,356
不！
No!

89
00:07:07,059 --> 00:07:09,050
海莉
Hayley!

90
00:07:38,324 --> 00:07:39,313
不
No.

91
00:07:50,102 --> 00:07:52,502
她死了
She's gone.

92
00:08:04,517 --> 00:08:06,781
你被咬了
KLAUS: You've been bitten.

93
00:08:22,068 --> 00:08:24,730
这些只够一个人喝
There's only enough here for one.

94
00:08:24,904 --> 00:08:26,667
不，一定够的
No. This has to be enough.

95
00:08:43,189 --> 00:08:45,180
我没法选择
I can't choose.

96
00:08:46,659 --> 00:08:48,024
求求你别逼我做选择
Please don't make me choose.

97
00:08:54,400 --> 00:08:56,027
去救你的朋友吧
Save your friend.

98
00:08:58,037 --> 00:08:59,629
我来照顾其他人
I can take care of the rest of us.

99
00:08:59,805 --> 00:09:01,500
- 马赛尔
- 我不要
-Marcel.
-I can't.

100
00:09:01,674 --> 00:09:03,835
看看你的伤口
你没时间废话了
Judging by the look of that bite,
you don't have time to argue.

101
00:09:04,010 --> 00:09:05,807
马赛尔
Marcel.

102
00:09:05,978 --> 00:09:08,412
小约是我的人
Josh is one of my guys.

103
00:09:08,581 --> 00:09:12,540
今天我的人死得够多了
快喝吧
Enough of my guys have died today,
so come on.

104
00:09:21,127 --> 00:09:22,321
你得一分
One point for you...

105
00:09:24,864 --> 00:09:27,662
尼克劳斯也得一分
and one point for Niklaus. (ECHOlNG)

106
00:09:40,346 --> 00:09:43,144
嘿
你要去哪？
Hey.
Where do you think you're going?

107
00:09:43,316 --> 00:09:47,480
去找克劳斯，拿他的血
尽全力救我的手下
To find Klaus, get his blood, and
save as many of my guys as I can.

108
00:09:47,653 --> 00:09:49,587
等等
Wait.

109
00:09:50,790 --> 00:09:52,883
这样的话，你需要武器
For that, you'll need a weapon.

110
00:09:53,059 --> 00:09:55,857
正好我有个武器库
And it just so happens
I have an arsenal.

111
00:10:07,840 --> 00:10:11,105
- 怎么会这样？
- 我被打败了
-How?
-I was bested.

112
00:10:11,277 --> 00:10:14,178
你被打败了？
You were bested?

113
00:10:19,285 --> 00:10:24,154
你…
居然会被打败！
You were bested!

114
00:10:25,725 --> 00:10:26,817
我战无不胜的弟弟
My invincible brother.

115
00:10:33,733 --> 00:10:37,430
她们带走了孩子，但还有时间
They took the baby
but there's still time.

116
00:10:37,603 --> 00:10:40,663
我们可以救她
We can save her.

117
00:10:45,378 --> 00:10:47,778
墓地都空了，这地方都荒废了
她不在这里
Tombs are empty, the grounds
are deserted. She's not here!

118
00:10:47,947 --> 00:10:50,381
她们只可能来这
我们要继续找
This is the only place they can be.
We'll keep searching.

119
00:10:50,549 --> 00:10:52,517
她们不在这里，尼克劳斯
我们在浪费时间
They are not here, Niklaus.
We're wasting time!

120
00:10:52,685 --> 00:10:55,245
她们的收获仪式在这里
收割仪式也在这里
Their harvest was here,
the reaping was here.

121
00:10:55,421 --> 00:10:58,618
她们现在就要举行仪式
去祭祀她们的祖先
They are about to perform a ritual which
will feed their ancestors for centuries,

122
00:10:58,791 --> 00:11:01,851
而她们的祖先就是埋在这里的
ancestors who are buried here.

123
00:11:06,799 --> 00:11:09,324
这个雕像
This statue.

124
00:11:09,502 --> 00:11:14,235
我们已经路过它三次了
我们一直都是朝同一个方向走
We've passed by this three times, all
whilst going in the same direction.

125
00:11:27,787 --> 00:11:29,914
她们一定施了某种幻觉咒语了
They have fabricated
some kind of illusion.

126
00:11:37,129 --> 00:11:38,357
看来你说得没错
That's one word for it.

127
00:12:01,187 --> 00:12:04,156
- 这就是基兰隐藏的东西
- 说储藏更确切点
-So this is what Kieran was hiding.
-More like stockpiling.

128
00:12:04,323 --> 00:12:06,621
我看了一下，基本上都是些武器
From what I can gather,
it's mostly weapons.

129
00:12:06,792 --> 00:12:09,158
都是女巫制造出来的黑暗魔物
Dark objects created by witches.

130
00:12:09,328 --> 00:12:10,852
被人类所借用
And co-opted by the humans.

131
00:12:12,631 --> 00:12:15,065
基兰多年来一直守着这个秘密
Kieran's been keeping this
a secret for years.

132
00:12:15,234 --> 00:12:17,099
你确定要给我看这些东西吗？
You sure you want to show me all this?

133
00:12:17,269 --> 00:12:20,864
你说过得知我叔叔的秘密会害我丧命
You said knowing my uncle's secrets
could get me killed.

134
00:12:21,040 --> 00:12:24,441
但要是这些秘密能拯救我的朋友呢？
But what if those same secrets
could save the lives of my friends?

135
00:12:24,610 --> 00:12:26,942
看这个
我在学校里学过
Look at this.
I learned about it in the Lycee.

136
00:12:27,113 --> 00:12:28,944
它叫做恶魔之星
It's called the Devil's Star.

137
00:12:29,115 --> 00:12:31,242
据说投掷一次就能造成一千道伤口
They say one throw
can make a thousand cuts.

138
00:12:31,417 --> 00:12:35,217
一千道伤口听起来不错
我就是要让克劳斯流血
A thousand cuts sounds about right.
I need to make Klaus bleed.

139
00:12:42,895 --> 00:12:43,919
这东西太妙了
It's ingenious.

140
00:12:44,096 --> 00:12:47,588
我看得见它们，也感觉得到它们
但它们并不存在
I can see them, I can feel them,
and yet they are not real.

141
00:12:47,767 --> 00:12:48,791
一定有办法
There has to be a way.

142
00:12:48,968 --> 00:12:52,096
- 要是能直接离开这里就好了
- 我们需要集中精力
-Even if we could just push through--
-What we need to do is focus.

143
00:12:52,271 --> 00:12:54,432
我现在唯一关心的就是孩子和她的安危
My only focus right now is that child
and her safety.

144
00:12:54,607 --> 00:12:55,733
你懂吗？
Do you understand me?

145
00:12:55,908 --> 00:12:57,000
这一切
This, all of this.

146
00:12:57,176 --> 00:12:59,667
这一切就是你创造的世界，尼克劳斯
This is the world
that you created, Niklaus.

147
00:12:59,812 --> 00:13:01,473
- 哥哥
- 你的那些阴谋
-Brother--
-All of your scheming,

148
00:13:01,647 --> 00:13:04,707
你可悲的一生每天都在树敌
the enemies that you have made
every day of your miserable life.

149
00:13:04,884 --> 00:13:06,442
你还指望有什么结果？
What results did you expect?

150
00:13:06,652 --> 00:13:08,916
你难道觉得你的孩子能过着幸福的生活
That your child would be born
into a happy life?

151
00:13:09,088 --> 00:13:12,023
而她的母亲可以好好活着
看着她长大吗？
That the mother would be alive
to know her daughter?

152
00:13:12,191 --> 00:13:14,955
亦或我们可以像普通家庭一样
安定地生活？
That we could live and thrive
as some sort of family?

153
00:13:15,127 --> 00:13:18,756
- 那是你的幻想，不是我的！
- 不！弟弟。

154
00:13:18,931 --> 00:13:20,990
这曾是我们的希望
This was our hope.

155
00:13:21,167 --> 00:13:23,158
是我们家的希望
This was our family's hope.

156
00:13:25,971 --> 00:13:27,165
但现在她不在了
And now she is gone.

157
00:13:28,407 --> 00:13:32,741
你明白吗？
我让她进入了我的生活
Do you understand?
I let this person in.

158
00:13:35,114 --> 00:13:37,548
我接纳了她
I let her in.

159
00:13:37,716 --> 00:13:40,184
我从不接纳任何人的
I don't let people in.

160
00:13:40,352 --> 00:13:44,015
你明知道这一点
却还是将她从我身边夺走
You knew this,
and you've taken her from me.

161
00:13:47,493 --> 00:13:49,984
我需要她，而你毁了我
I needed her,
and you've broken me.

162
00:14:10,382 --> 00:14:11,940
等我们救下你侄女
You can tell your niece

163
00:14:12,117 --> 00:14:17,885
你可以告诉她
你有多在乎她母亲
how much you cared for her mother
when we save her.

164
00:14:54,560 --> 00:14:55,720
用力
Push.

165
00:14:59,131 --> 00:15:01,429
不！
No!

166
00:15:14,546 --> 00:15:17,310
天快亮了，月亮差不多隐没了
The moon has almost faded
from the morning sky.

167
00:15:21,453 --> 00:15:23,284
我得做好准备
I need to prepare.

168
00:15:31,764 --> 00:15:34,699
她一定会进行到底
祖先们已保证她会活下去
She'll go through with it.
