How are you here?

195
00:18:26,071 --> 00:18:30,735
我在教堂里醒来
我感觉到饥饿
I woke up in the church.
I felt this hunger.

196
00:18:32,611 --> 00:18:34,340
我知道我需要什么
I knew what I needed.

197
00:18:37,883 --> 00:18:39,908
我感觉得到她
I can feel her.

198
00:18:41,920 --> 00:18:43,717
她就在这里
She's here.

199
00:18:44,823 --> 00:18:46,620
我感觉得到我的孩子
I can feel my baby.

200
00:18:48,293 --> 00:18:51,729
你死的时候，孩子的血还在你体内
You died with the baby's blood
still in your system.

201
00:18:53,298 --> 00:18:55,425
她正在转变
She's in transition.

202
00:18:56,668 --> 00:19:00,968
