必须喝孩子的血
Which means she has to drink the
blood of the child if she's to survive.

203
00:19:02,307 --> 00:19:04,775
这样才能成为混合种
To be a reborn hybrid.

204
00:19:06,778 --> 00:19:08,609
我不在乎自己
I don't care about me.

205
00:19:11,316 --> 00:19:12,874
