I'm going to go find our daughter.

206
00:19:21,894 --> 00:19:24,795
尘灰成骨
骨肉重组
From ash to bone,
from bone to flesh,

207
00:19:24,963 --> 00:19:26,430
魂归人间
from flesh to life.

208
00:19:56,795 --> 00:19:58,456
不！
No!

209
00:20:10,676 --> 00:20:11,904
