This bite.

223
00:22:54,706 --> 00:22:56,469
所有的这一切
All this.

224
00:22:58,944 --> 00:23:00,912
我知道不是没有原因的
I know it didn't come from nowhere.

225
00:23:02,848 --> 00:23:08,480
一个世纪前，我把你父亲引来这里
开始了这一切
This is the last note in a song
that I started a century ago.

226
00:23:10,822 --> 00:23:13,313
如今到了结局之时
When I brought your dad to town.

227
00:23:15,794 --> 00:23:18,888
为此，我很抱歉
And for that, I am sorry.

228
00:23:23,902 --> 00:23:25,893
不
No.

229
00:23:26,071 --> 00:23:30,030
你救了我孩子的命，马赛尔
You saved my child's life, Marcel.

230
00:23:32,344 --> 00:23:36,781
因此
这是你应得的
For that, you deserve this.

231
00:23:44,489 --> 00:23:49,222
我们会打倒
造成这一切的罪魁祸首
We will take down
whoever brought this upon us.

232
00:23:53,298 --> 00:23:54,822
