Why is this happening?

238
00:26:07,632 --> 00:26:09,395
你复活我是为了杀我儿子
You brought me back to kill my son.

239
00:26:09,568 --> 00:26:11,365
我复活你是为了惩罚他
I brought you back to punish him.

240
00:26:11,536 --> 00:26:14,164
等我准备好了你自然会有机会
And you will when I'm ready
and not a minute before.

241
00:26:14,339 --> 00:26:18,503
你到底做了什么？
What have you done?

242
00:26:20,145 --> 00:26:24,411
我在你的复活咒语里加了点别的东西
I added a little something extra
in the spell that brought you back.

243
00:26:24,583 --> 00:26:28,883
我耗费了八个月的生命
待在这当秘密武器
I spent eight months of my life here
being used as a secret weapon.

244
00:26:29,988 --> 00:26:32,047
现在你也能体会一下这感受
Now you can see how it feels.

245
00:26:34,626 --> 00:26:35,718
跪下
Kneel.

246
00:26:44,469 --> 00:26:45,561
为什么？
Why?

247
00:26:45,737 --> 00:26:47,364
祖先们没有给我选择的余地
The ancestors left me no choice.

248
00:26:47,539 --> 00:26:50,906
你想牺牲一个无辜的婴儿
以获得更多力量
You were willing to sacrifice
an innocent baby for more power.

249
00:26:51,076 --> 00:26:53,044
不只是力量
Oh, not just power.

250
00:26:53,211 --> 00:26:55,076
那是祖先的决定
It was the ancestors' decree.

251
00:26:56,615 --> 00:26:57,912
是她的决定
It was her decree.

252
00:27:00,085 --> 00:27:02,315
谁的决定？
It was whose decree?

253
00:27:02,487 --> 00:27:04,717
我很惊讶你会这么问
I'm surprised you have to ask.

254
00:27:05,924 --> 00:27:08,757
毕竟正是你说服了你的弟弟妹妹
After all, you were the one
who convinced your siblings

255
00:27:08,927 --> 00:27:10,952
在纽奥良的土地上将她献祭
to consecrate her
in New Orleans soil.

256
00:27:12,797 --> 00:27:14,287
艾丝塔
Esther.

257
00:27:17,736 --> 00:27:24,403
所以即便死亡也无法阻止我母亲
灭绝她亲骨肉的决心
So not even death can stop my mother
from seeking the annihilation
of her own flesh and blood.

258
00:27:24,576 --> 00:27:26,806
这并不是终结
This isn't the end.

259
00:27:26,978 --> 00:27:28,605
只要那个孩子还活着
As long as that child lives,

260
00:27:28,780 --> 00:27:31,874
纽奥良的女巫就不会停止追杀她
the witches of New Orleans
will never stop coming for it.

261
00:27:32,050 --> 00:27:35,713
艾丝塔永远不会停止追杀她
Esther will never stop
coming for it.

262
00:27:35,887 --> 00:27:37,286
