It has been decreed.

263
00:27:37,455 --> 00:27:40,424
你的孩子将被献祭给祖先们
Your baby will be consecrated
among her ancestors.

264
00:27:40,592 --> 00:27:42,287
她活不了的
She will not live.

265
00:27:44,529 --> 00:27:47,794
他们也来找我了
我能感觉到
They're coming for me.
I can feel it.

266
00:27:47,966 --> 00:27:49,957
我让他们失望了
I've failed them.

267
00:27:51,269 --> 00:27:53,294
求求你们
Please.

268
00:27:53,471 --> 00:27:55,962
请理解，我只是想活下去
Understand, I just wanted to live.

269
00:27:57,075 --> 00:28:02,172
告诉克劳斯
我很抱歉
Tell Klaus I'm sorry.

270
00:28:11,289 --> 00:28:13,814
我可不
I'm not.

271
00:28:24,769 --> 00:28:26,669
（杜曼街）

272
00:28:28,640 --> 00:28:31,131
我们早该察觉母亲与这事有关的
We should have felt
our mother's hand in this.

273
00:28:31,309 --> 00:28:33,209
我们早该知道
We should have known
she would not be bound

274
00:28:33,378 --> 00:28:35,107
死亡也无法阻止她的
by anything as obvious as death.

275
00:28:35,280 --> 00:28:38,340
如今她控制了女巫
and now she has control
of the witches.

276
00:28:38,516 --> 00:28:40,916
- 她们不会停手的
- 对
-They will never stop.
-No.

277
00:28:41,086 --> 00:28:42,849
葛雷拉家族也不会善罢甘休的
Nor would I expect
the Guerrera Wolves to back down.

278
00:28:43,021 --> 00:28:46,184
海莉和孩子是狼人中的皇室
Hayley and the child
are wolf royalty.

279
00:28:46,357 --> 00:28:50,987
因此她们对佛朗西丝卡的统治
就是一种威胁
And as such, they are a threat
to Francesca's claim to leadership.

280
00:28:51,162 --> 00:28:52,527
她们永远不会安全的
They will never be safe.

281
