你之前对我怎么说的
What was it you said to me earlier,

282
00:28:58,169 --> 00:29:01,764
我可悲的一生每天都在树敌？
that I've made enemies
every day of my miserable life?

283
00:29:01,940 --> 00:29:04,966
最可怕的敌人就在我们身边，哥哥
Well, the worst of them
are within these borders, brother.

284
00:29:06,678 --> 00:29:09,613
我为世界带来了一个可以对付我的武器
I have brought into the world
a weapon they can use against me.

285
00:29:09,781 --> 00:29:11,976
那我们就武装好自己
ELlJAH: Then we will arm ourselves.

286
00:29:12,150 --> 00:29:15,449
