Brother, we fought every adversary
in this town and we have won.

287
00:29:15,620 --> 00:29:18,555
不论对手是谁
我们会再次和他们交手
We'll fight them again,
no matter who they are.

288
00:29:18,723 --> 00:29:20,850
我们要把这个家变成坚实的堡垒
We'll make this home a fortress.

289
00:29:21,025 --> 00:29:24,153
我不会让她过囚犯一样的生活
I will not have her live her life
as a prisoner.

290
00:29:24,329 --> 00:29:26,820
那就离开这里，我们一起走
Then we leave here together,
all of us.

291
00:29:26,998 --> 00:29:30,729
无论我们去哪
无论逃到多远
Wherever we go, however far we run,

292
00:29:30,902 --> 00:29:35,862
