She has inherited all our enemies
with none of our defenses.

294
00:29:40,512 --> 00:29:43,174
所以不论我们是留下还是离开
她都备受威胁
So whether we stay or we leave,
we condemn her.

295
00:29:43,348 --> 00:29:45,612
还有第三个选择
HAYLEY: There is a third option.

296
00:29:48,953 --> 00:29:51,945
我在战争的环境中长大
I grew up in a war zone.

297
00:29:52,123 --> 00:29:54,887
