就是送走她
I think the only thing to do
is send her away

309
00:30:52,851 --> 00:30:54,182
我们自己留下来
while we stay behind

310
00:30:54,352 --> 00:30:56,684
收拾好我们制造的烂摊子
and clean up the mess
that we've made.

311
