We will work together

326
00:31:53,978 --> 00:31:59,041
保证“新月城”纽奥良市
再次繁荣
to ensure the heart
of the Crescent City thrives again.

327
00:32:11,963 --> 00:32:13,055
坚持到最后的人
Last man standing, huh?

328
00:32:15,833 --> 00:32:17,460
