00:32:51,869 --> 00:32:55,566
一群瘦弱的吸血鬼那边
with a pack of scrawny vamps...

340
00:32:56,607 --> 00:32:59,167
还是他创造的新狼族大军这边呢？
...or an army of the new wolf breed
that he created?

341
00:32:59,344 --> 00:33:02,074
我想他会站在我们这边的
I'm thinking
he's gonna side with us.

342
00:33:02,246 --> 00:33:06,444
尤其是当他发现
你们的族人杀死了他的孩子
Especially after he finds out
that your pack killed his kid.

343
00:33:08,553 --> 00:33:09,952
什么？
What?

344
00:33:11,456 --> 00:33:12,480
打开箱子
Open the box,

345
00:33:12,657 --> 00:33:14,648
告诉我你觉得克劳斯会认为
and let me know
what you think Klaus will believe

346
00:33:14,826 --> 00:33:17,351
谁该为箱子里的东西负责
about who's responsible
for what you find inside of it.

347
00:33:24,569 --> 00:33:29,199
火化也许是最好的方式
趁克劳斯还没追查到你之前
Cremation may be the best way to go
before Klaus smells it on you.

348
00:33:56,334 --> 00:33:58,495
（我们想你）

349
00:34:01,339 --> 00:34:03,637
（悼念米卡森宝宝）

350
00:34:09,947 --> 00:34:11,505
克劳斯
CAMl: Klaus.

351
00:34:16,988 --> 00:34:19,013
孩子？
The baby?

352
00:34:19,190 --> 00:34:21,124
她死了
She died.

353
00:34:21,292 --> 00:34:23,658
在葛雷拉发动攻击几小时之后
A few hours
after the Guerrera attack.

354
00:34:25,530 --> 00:34:27,964
这…
这都是我的错
This is--
This is all my fault.

355
00:34:28,132 --> 00:34:30,498
- 我向你保证，不是你的错
- 不
-I can assure you it is not.
-No.

356
00:34:30,668 --> 00:34:32,932
如果我没有迟疑
If I hadn't hesitated,

357
00:34:33,104 --> 00:34:35,299
我就能及时揭穿佛朗西丝卡的阴谋
阻止这一切
I could have uncovered
Francesca's plot in time to stop it.

358
00:34:35,473 --> 00:34:39,273
那你要如何阻止女巫与她联手？
And how would you have stopped the
coven of witches in league with her?

359
00:34:40,478 --> 00:34:41,843
不
No.

360
00:34:43,281 --> 00:34:48,617
如果要怪谁，一定是我
If anyone is to blame, I am.

361
00:34:50,621 --> 00:34:54,853
我真的很抱歉
I am so, so sorry.

362
00:34:58,396 --> 00:35:00,523
卡蜜儿
Camille.

363
00:35:03,067 --> 00:35:07,527
我感谢你能来这里
但我们不能成为朋友
I appreciate you being here,
but we cannot be friends.

364
00:35:07,705 --> 00:35:10,230
什么？
What?

365
00:35:10,408 --> 00:35:12,899
你一开始就说对了
You had me pegged from the start.

366
00:35:13,077 --> 00:35:16,706
我被自己的恶魔摧毁了
那些恶魔还在纠缠不休
A man damaged by his demons,
and those demons are not dormant.

367
00:35:16,881 --> 00:35:21,443
他们下定决心要杀死我
还有我眼里美好的一切
They are hell-bent on killing me
and everything I find beautiful.

368
00:35:23,955 --> 00:35:25,786
而你
And you.

369
00:35:28,126 --> 00:35:30,287
你那么美好
You are beautiful.

370
00:35:32,797 --> 00:35:35,322
求求你
Please.

371
00:35:35,500 --> 00:35:37,024
- 求你走吧
- 克劳斯
-Please just go.
-Klaus.

372
00:35:38,603 --> 00:35:40,662
走吧
Go.

373
00:36:01,359 --> 00:36:02,917
马赛尔的任务完成了吗？
Did Marcel play his part?

374
00:36:03,094 --> 00:36:05,358
他在路易斯安那州北部的一家医院里
He managed
to locate a stillborn baby

375
00:36:05,530 --> 00:36:07,430
找到了一个胎死腹中的孩子
in a hospital in upstate Louisiana.

376
00:36:07,598 --> 00:36:09,463
我想他是接受我们的条件了
I trust he agreed to the terms.

377
00:36:09,634 --> 00:36:11,625
他同意让我魅惑他
He has agreed
to allow me to compel him

378
00:36:11,802 --> 00:36:15,101
忘记我孩子的事情
to forget what he knows of my child.

379
00:36:15,273 --> 00:36:17,434
交换是，他要几小瓶我的血液
In exchange,
he wants vials of my blood.

380
00:36:17,608 --> 00:36:20,042
必须让女巫相信才行
But the witches
will have to believe this.

381
00:36:20,211 --> 00:36:23,703
第四名收获祭女孩很快就会复活
Soon that fourth harvest girl
will resurrect.

382
00:36:23,881 --> 00:36:25,712
女巫又将复原
The coven will rebuild.

383
00:36:25,883 --> 00:36:28,579
要是她们察觉你的孩子还活着
她们会追杀她的
If they sense that your child lives,
they will hunt her.

384
00:36:28,753 --> 00:36:31,017
女巫们会相信我们说的话
The witches will buy what we sell.

385
00:36:32,990 --> 00:36:36,153
只要我们能自圆其说
We just have to sell it properly.

386
00:36:44,902 --> 00:36:49,305
那就只剩下道别了
Well, then all that remains
is to say goodbye.

387
00:37:33,050 --> 00:37:37,316
他们会看着我们
所有人
KLAUS: They will be watching us,
all of them.

388
00:37:38,789 --> 00:37:43,055
我们三人一起离开会引来许多注意
The three of us leaving together
will draw too much attention.

389
00:37:43,227 --> 00:37:45,388
我会独自离开
I will go alone.

390
00:37:46,964 --> 00:37:50,764
我走了之后，你们要参加公众追悼会
Take your mourning public
when I'm gone.

391
00:37:50,935 --> 00:37:53,529
我想那不会太难的
I don't imagine
that will be too difficult.

392
00:37:54,672 --> 00:37:58,574
毕竟，悲伤的情绪是真的
Grief, after all, is grief.

393
00:38:03,114 --> 00:38:07,278
离开我们她要在哪才会安全，弟弟？
ELlJAH: In what world will she
be safe without us, brother?

394
00:38:07,451 --> 00:38:09,078
谁能比我们提供更好的保护给她？
Who can protect her better than we?

395
00:38:11,522 --> 00:38:13,752
有一个人能
KLAUS: There is one person.

396
00:38:26,203 --> 00:38:28,034
你好，妹妹
Hello, sister.

397
00:38:34,879 --> 00:38:37,404
她长得像她妈妈
Oh, she looks like her mother.

398
00:38:40,017 --> 00:38:42,417
也许真的有上帝
Maybe there is a God after all.

399
00:38:44,855 --> 00:38:48,382
她的眼里看得到些许恶魔的影子
Well, she has a hint of the devil
in her eyes.

400
00:38:49,660 --> 00:38:50,718
那是遗传我的
That's all me.

401
00:38:54,999 --> 00:38:59,095
你需要一个可以信赖的女巫
施个隐身咒
You'll need a witch you can trust
to cast a cloaking spell.

402
00:38:59,270 --> 00:39:00,669
我会找到的
I'll get one.

403
00:39:00,838 --> 00:39:03,306
- 不能让任何人发现她
- 我知道该怎么做，尼克
-No one can ever find her.
-I know what to do, Nik.

404
00:39:06,377 --> 00:39:10,677
也许我们会建起白色的篱笆
我想那一定会很美
Perhaps we'll get a white fence.
I think that would be lovely.

405
00:39:22,593 --> 00:39:26,359
这个城市以为你死了
This city would have seen you dead,

406
00:39:26,530 --> 00:39:28,896
但我会把这里变成你的家
but I will have it your home.

407
00:39:29,066 --> 00:39:35,767
每一个想要伤害你的人
都会被杀死
And every soul who wishes you harm
will be struck down.

408
00:39:35,940 --> 00:39:40,274
只要你的血脉里还流着我的血
Just as sure
as my blood runs in your veins,

409
00:39:40,444 --> 00:39:44,437
你就会回到我身边
you will return to me.

410
00:40:07,571 --> 00:40:09,368
尽管我们之间有矛盾，蕾贝卡
In spite of our differences,
Rebekah,

411
00:40:09,540 --> 00:40:12,407
但把女儿交给你，我最放心
there is no one I would trust more
with my daughter's life.

412
00:40:19,717 --> 00:40:23,118
要幸福，妹妹
Be happy, sister.

413
00:40:24,555 --> 00:40:26,455
她会幸福的，尼克，我保证
She will be happy, Nik. I promise.

414
00:40:28,592 --> 00:40:30,753
她叫什么名字？
What's her name?

415
00:40:35,032 --> 00:40:36,761
希望
Hope.

416
00:40:38,702 --> 00:40:41,102
她叫希望
Her name is Hope.

417
00:41:27,251 --> 00:41:30,880
愿你安息
MAN: May you rest in peace.

418
00:41:31,055 --> 00:41:32,579
那有什么意思？
WOMAN: What's the fun in that?

419
00:41:35,159 --> 00:41:38,026
来吧，我们有许多事要做
Come along. We have much to do.

420
00:41:40,397 --> 00:41:41,659
是的，母亲
Yes mother.

421
00:41:47,004 --> 00:41:52,032
（艾丝塔 我们敬爱的母亲）

422
00:41:52,409 --> 00:41:57,938
片名：创始吸血鬼（第一季）

